snippet.title: VaporWave Pinball Demo Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST ON STEAM HERE:

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2465930/Vaporwave_Pinball/

Lose yourself inside liminal vaporwave environments whilst playing digital pinball.

Use the inbuilt Video Home Operating System ver. 92 to discover new virtual locations and exciting tables.

Uncover corrupted files that are perhaps best not opened.

Flip your way to beat your own high score or simply relax in the 90s void.

Designed to play for a few minutes at a time or to lose several hours to.

Featuring a custom vaporwave soundtrack and custom assets.



Made by Mixtape Games, a solo developer from London.
